!     *        JOHN ADAMS, PAUL SWARZTRAUBER AND ROLAND SWEET         *
!     *                                                               *
!     *                             OF                                *
!     *                                                               *
!     *         THE NATIONAL CENTER FOR ATMOSPHERIC RESEARCH          *
