          ' RETURNED VALUE OF IFLAG AND RESIDUAL NORM', I5, E20.5 /)
 9020 FORMAT (/' **********WARNING -- SOS FAILED SOME TESTS**********')
 9030 FORMAT (/' ----------SOS PASSED ALL TESTS----------')
end
